column4: I like to snuggle and to sneeze.
I can't start my day without my morning coffee.
If I barf, I eat, no trace, no waste.
They say I can't eat choclate, I say you can't prevent me.
If I don't go out every two hours, I'll pee on the rug.
Whether you like it or not, I'll snuff your butt!
I Like to play fetch in the park every evening!
I like to run after things and bite them.
my favorite color is green, red :p
Really, I'm a wolf in disguise.
Can you tell the people that made this don't have dogs?
I see myself as a singer, especially at 2am.
I'm dark, Ihowl to the moon.
